751220","type":"paragraph","text":"这个争论（即真理标准的讨论──引者注）很好，越看越好，是政治问题，是国家命运问题。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b08b27f59f","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于发扬民主加强法制）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9168b10e0","type":"paragraph","text":"在现在这个时期更要加强民主。集中多少年，现在是民主不够，不敢讲，心有余悸。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b757846e8f","type":"paragraph","text":"发展经济，民主选举，民主管理，民主监督。工厂工人监督，农村社员监督。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70a9831d6d","type":"paragraph","text":"目前主要是反对空头政治……反对说空话。现在是正确的意见，也不落实，没有具体措施，一拖就是一年。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69c258c379","type":"paragraph","text":"讲权力下放，企业。讲讲千方百计，讲调动积极性。利用每一寸土地，有一点土地种一棵树，有一块水面搞养殖，有一块草原种草。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce44e0ace2","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于自主权与国家计划的矛盾）","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9687fd2dea","type":"paragraph","text":"这个矛盾只能从价值法则供求关系来调整。……否则不能自主，靠质量，质量好销全国。不要怕，乱，乱不出来（承认市场一定调节）。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"714377ec21","type":"paragraph","text":"经济民主，重点不是政治，重点是经济民主。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3abe061bc","type":"paragraph","text":"有些要用法律，民法，刑法，各种单行法，植树应该有法律。地方也可以立法。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e82c909ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于向前看）","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ab5b609de","type":"paragraph","text":"这个会议向后看解决一些问题，目的是为了向前看，不要一刀切，解决遗留问题，快，干净利落，时间不要长。完全满意不可能。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9e59602e7","type":"paragraph","text":"安定团结十分重要。……毛主席文化大革命中问题，不纠缠这个问题。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30bde55fe3","type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命，不要涉及，让时间来说清，过一段时间再说这个问题，没有一点吃亏。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e2462ef81","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈克服官僚主义）","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7400bfa5ca","type":"paragraph","text":"学会管理，培养与选用人才，使用人才，改革规章制度。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f70c0fff9","type":"paragraph","text":"好的企业必须用先进的办法管理企业。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f4769a9a2","type":"paragraph","text":"党委领导好不好，看企业管得好不好，利润，工人收入，城市如此，农村如此，各行各业如此。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d8cf2b6d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈允许一部分企业、地区、社员先好起来）","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6313a0927","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个大政策。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dedb903095","type":"paragraph","text":"允许一部分先富起来，农村５－１０－２０％；城市２０％，才有市场。本身就促进就开辟新行业。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eabffbef9b","type":"paragraph","text":"反对平均主义。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e087f1d428","type":"paragraph","text":"干得好的，就影响左邻右舍。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64ee25fea9","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于加强责任制）","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","publication":{},"articl